{"tid":1634202,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"愈諗愈嬲 說好的eye for an eye呢","createTime":"2019-10-07T06:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T07:27:59.000Z","uid":26763,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e5ef6c2d75b1f9c1d040fc74408c6b52c4bc06e1","tid":1634202,"uid":26763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:55:51.000Z","msg":"尋日個個廢老司機咁都可以唔洗死   第日好番一樣行得走得 再過黎車9你哋都得啊  女義士就要終身殘廢   公平咩   大家係咪唔記得當初話要eye for an eye啊 ？唔關自己事所以又算啊？我係警察都笑9你哋無膽正柒頭啦 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我認為 我哋要訂明神獸準則<br />\n<br />\n以後敢傷害義士嘅  <br />\n輕則圍毆<br />\n重則挖眼啦 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n捉到人即刻挖返一隻出黎 跟手都唔好再打啦 咪唔會成面血咁 畫面唔好睇又無成效 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋挖完仲可以即刻叫firstaid 包番好佢 既有意義又有成效 講得出做得到 eye for an eye</span></span> 我哋依家講到明 班popo啊藍絲啊自己好自為之啦 以後真係見唔到孫仔孫女個樣唔好怪我哋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Eye for an eye</span></span>"},{"pid":"2738ac1b2c7330d186795bffeafb3b9fcec56e50","tid":1634202,"uid":159762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:58:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港警察濫權實錄資料庫</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSnwmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=5d502b54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有英文同日文版 大家落力share俾更多外國人睇！！</span>"},{"pid":"2059d3d3b390f9a6d37e1b732e31c4bebbc16a1f","tid":1634202,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:59:21.000Z","msg":"其實應該揾人綁佢喺地下<br />\n揸佢架車碌斷佢對腳"},{"pid":"f7834c8fbe6812857bc5b780a34fcb4e291bc9a0","tid":1634202,"uid":256393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:00:42.000Z","msg":"車人腳 一齊企上佢隻腳<br />\n斬人手 一齊企上佢隻手"},{"pid